document_data.Notable Spellbooks:
[[File:Arcanabula-3e.jpg|thumb|''A working spellbook, or arcanabula, containing research notes and markings.'']]
* ''[[Tar'Ael Veluuthra]]'', a spellbook made for the [[Eldreth Veluuthra]], which contained spells to aid spying and movement{{Cite web/Tar'Ael Veluuthra}}
* The ''[[Demonomicon of Iggwilv|Demonomicon]]'' of [[Iggwilv]] contained several spells of her own creation, all related with controlling and binding [[demon]]s.{{Cite dungeon/148/Wells of Darkness|80-81}}
